      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/gold-xauusd-steadies-before-us-inflation-data-as-recession-fears-linger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，在美国关键数据公布之前，金价企稳，交易员关注的是他们是否会加强对美联储将很快转向货币宽松的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/gold-xauusd-steadies-before-us-inflation-data-as-recession-fears-linger</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 01:24:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
